item.title: Help!
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

Well what you do is try logging in, if it doesnt work then WAIT A FEW SECONDS and try it again. If it still doesnt work then your account may be on the banned users list in the “data” folder. If it still doesn’t work and its not in that file, then you need to reset your account if you really want to use it (delete the file of your username from these folders: “characters”, “connected from”, “moreinfo”, and "savedGames:). This should make it work. If it still doesnt yet then go into client.java and hit cntrl+f, then put your name in it (no underscores, use spaces) and keep searching and see if you put your name down for any “frame” commands. If you did, then delet it and replace it with either x91 or admin. (x91 preferred). If all of these things still dont make it work, then your server will be bad. THESE WILL WORK IF YOUR SERVER IS ANY GOOD. Enjoy and I hope this helps you! =)
